title: Unconditional Love: A love that lasts
description:
We all have been through hardships in our lives and we face challenges regularly. In our hardships, we can choose to fall down or stand up. Stand up and make a difference in your life. You have a choice!

The book presents original insights and practical advice that you can use to improve your financial, physical and emotional states. There are three stages for unconditional love. Applying them will help you improve your happiness and fulfilment. In turn, you can share that feeling with those around you to create a loving environment.
